<li><a href="/wiki/Nicholas_Maxwell" title="Nicholas Maxwell">Maxwell, Nicholas</a>, <i>The Comprehensibility of the Universe: A New Conception of Science</i>, Oxford University Press, Oxford, 1998. Paperback 2003.</li>
